should be closed by 15th March 2024.

183
00:08:21,620 --> 00:08:23,273
Nodal accounts are those accounts

184
00:08:23,273 --> 00:08:26,563
which are used by e-commerce and online services businesses.

185
00:08:26,563 --> 00:08:28,839
And as far as Paytm Wallet is concerned,

186
00:08:28,839 --> 00:08:30,914
you can use your existing balance

187
00:08:30,914 --> 00:08:32,493
but after 29th February,

188
00:08:32,493 --> 00:08:34,434
