198
00:08:55,418 --> 00:08:56,835
In November 2017,

199
00:08:56,835 --> 00:08:58,984
Paytm's Payments Bank was launched

200
00:08:58,984 --> 00:09:00,711
and in June 2018,

201
00:09:00,711 --> 00:09:02,781
