laundering regulations properly.

204
00:09:07,711 --> 00:09:11,510
And the identity of the customers 
who made their accounts with their bank

205
00:09:11,510 --> 00:09:13,089
was not being verified properly by Paytm.

206
00:09:13,089 --> 00:09:16,013
The KYC, or Know Your Customer compliance 

207
00:09:16,013 --> 00:09:18,112
wasn't adhered to by Paytm.

208
00:09:18,112 --> 00:09:22,472
So RBI told Paytm to stop onboarding new customers

209
00:09:22,472 --> 00:09:24,745
until it fixes all these issues.

210
00:09:24,745 --> 00:09:27,018
Paytm took some action regarding this warning

211
00:09:27,018 --> 00:09:28,599
because in January 2019,

212
00:09:28,599 --> 00:09:33,551
RBI allowed Paytm to resume onboarding customers.

213
